data.description: Discover this pristine residence nestled in the charming Swartz Creek community. Constructed in 2019 and finalized in 2020, this home exudes a timeless appeal that remains as fresh as the day it was built. Boasting 4 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, it offers ample space for comfortable living. With a serene backdrop of wooded surroundings, privacy is guaranteed. Conveniently located near shopping, dining, and expressways, this remarkable home is an absolute must-see. Don't miss out, schedule your showing today before it's too late!
